>>>>>>Global package<<<<
#Window
>  Run cmd as Admin
>  npm i -g create-react-app

#Mac/Linux
> open your terminal
> sudo npm i -g create-react-app


>>>>>>Setup React App<<<<<<<
#Window
>  Run cmd as Admin
>  npm i -g create-react-app
-----
>  Navigate to the folder using cmd
>  create-react-app myapp
>  cd myapp
>  npm start

#Mac/Linux
>  open your terminal
>  sudo npm i -g create-react-app
-----
>  Navigate to the folder using cmd
>  create-react-app myapp
>  cd myapp
>  npm start

